collections.name: NftRemixArt
collections.description:
NftRemixArt is a collection where art finds new life in the digital age. Inspired by a fusion of styles, it combines elements of Renaissance, Realism, Impressionism, Modern Art, Graffiti, and contemporary Abstraction to create unique artistic remixes.
Each piece is a dialogue between the past and the present, tradition and rebellious self-expression. Vibrant colors, textured layers, and dynamic compositions transform iconic images into modern digital art, while contemporary motifs take on the mysterious styles of past masters, available in NFT format.
Styles: Classical Art, Impressionism, Post-Impressionism, Modern Art, Suprematism, Cubism, Surrealism, Street Art, Digital Art
Format: NFT, digital painting, mixed media
Idea: to transform the legacy of art by reinterpreting it in the context of a new visual culture
NftRemixArt – where tradition meets digital revolution!

collections.name: Visions of Madness
collections.description:
"Visions of Madness" is a raw and unfiltered exploration of the chaotic depths of the human mind, where emotion, identity, and reality blur into a frenzy of distorted forms and vibrant colors. The exaggerated, melting faces and twisted expressions symbolize the struggle for self-expression in an overwhelming world, where thoughts spiral into disorder and emotions erupt without control. The bold, clashing hues against dark voids reflect the intensity of inner turmoil, mirroring both the beauty and terror of unrestrained creativity. Each sketch in this collection serves as a fragmented reflection of personal madness—a window into subconscious fears, desires, and unspoken anxieties. It is an artistic purge, a visual diary of raw thoughts translated into surreal abstraction, where chaos and creativity intertwine in a vivid spectacle of distorted perception.

My thoughts, my sketches and my madness. AI enhanced.

collections.name: Neon Donkey Protocol v1
collections.description:
Neon Donkey Protocol v1 is a glitchpunk PFP collection of anthropomorphic donkey avatars caught between satire, apathy, and digital collapse.

Each character is illustrated in high-resolution 2D, featuring clean vector outlines, exaggerated proportions, and a sarcastic disregard for the virtual world around them. Designed from the waist up, every donkey expresses some form of ironic detachment — a subtle rebellion in a universe that already gave up.

This collection is powered by the Aesthetic-Algorithmic System v1, an intentional blend of manual curation and procedural logic. The system defines visual categories, rarity distributions, and stylistic coherence while embracing chaos and absurdity.

Neon Donkey Protocol v1 is the first deployment of this aesthetic framework, a generative philosophy where each NFT is a glitch-born entity from the edge of the metaverse.
AI played a key role, not as an artist — but as a co-conspirator in aesthetic sabotage.

Welcome to v1.

In the world of digital art, where technology and creativity meet, we present to you the "Iron Titans" collection, a unique NFT collection dedicated to legendary tanks from history. This collection is not just a compilation of digital artworks but also a tribute to military history and engineering genius that shaped the course of wars and victories.

About the Collection
The Iron Titans are more than just digital collectibles. Each NFT represents a uniquely hand-designed tank, with details that bring their historical roles to life. From the first tanks that marched onto battlefields in World War I to modern combat vehicles that dominate today's battlefields, this collection offers a journey through time and technological advancement.
